#: in_1/part_preface.html:893
msgid ""
"<p>Guillaume Marceau, working with Kathi Fisler and Shriram, spent many "
"months\n"
"studying and improving the error messages in DrRacket. We are grateful for "
"his\n"
"amazing work.</p>"
